WEBVTT

00:02.117 --> 00:06.897
Across the globe, followers of Islam are beginning to observe the holy month of Ramadan...

00:07.159 --> 00:13.541
...in which believers dedicate time to reflection and prayer, fasting from sunrise to sunset.

00:13.879 --> 00:18.253
Many of the world's Muslims, estimated to number more than one and a half billion,...

00:18.623 --> 00:21.524
...will be immersing themselves in the Ramadan traditions...

00:21.776 --> 00:25.608
...including reading and reciting the Koran and giving to charity.

00:26.139 --> 00:30.832
For some it's time to head home, for others a chance to visit somewhere special.

00:31.675 --> 00:36.109
We came to Istanbul in order to feel the unique atmosphere of Ramadan here.

00:40.518 --> 00:42.180
The duration is a lunar month.

00:42.595 --> 00:46.879
Most countries are observing the start of this year's holy month on Wednesday.

00:47.697 --> 00:53.110
But for others, including parts of Africa and the Americas, Ramadan has already begun.

